<plot>In the middle of nowhere an old scientist works in a greenhouse on his dream: a mutated corn seed with the power to grow incredibly fast. He isn't very succesful, it's failure on failure. All the mixtures he uses only have dramatic results and the seeds get more and more afraid. One seed manages to escape by coincidence. His long journey in the big big world begins. The mixture the scientist gave him seems to be very powerful though, as it has the tendency to react with many kinds of fluids. With unexpected results.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?237973</url></doc>
